videos.description: Josh LeBlanc slips free under the basket and throws down a nasty one-handed slam.
videos.headline: LeBlanc rises for powerful jam

videos.description: Eric Paschall elevates over Georgetown defenders and flushes a monster slam.
videos.headline: Paschall skies for vicious slam

videos.description: Jessie Govan fights for the rebound and finishes through contact for an and-1 lay-in
videos.headline: Govan muscles through contact for and-1

videos.description: James Akinjo pulls all the tricks out of his bag as he throws a sick between-the-legs pass to Jessie Govan who nails a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Akinjo between-the-legs dime leads to Govan 3-pointer

videos.description: Georgetown pulls away from Villanova as Jessie Govan slams home a one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Govan rises for emphatic slam
